dct_title_s: Section 4 : cyclists road map of New Jersey
dct_description_sm: Covers New Jersey north from the Delaware River to Bedminster and east to Princeton. Shows roads by grade, condition, and quality. Relief shown by hachures. Oriented with north to the upper left. "Copyrighted 1890, by H.A. Benedict." "Copyrighted by J.B. Beers & Co., 1890." Includes key. "Section 4"--Verso.
dct_publisher_sm: N.Y. : Published by J.B. Beers & Co. ... for the N.J. Division L.A.W., c1890.
